{"tid":1399350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郭文貴指8.4香港實施戒嚴, 港府澄清全屬謠言","createTime":"2019-08-03T06:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T07:00:25.000Z","uid":134071,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1a6e30a5c15d399efa65be6ebd550d792c5ea9c0","tid":1399350,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:44:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190803/59892314\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190803%2F59892314&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=d713ed7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190803%2F59892314&h=ce9f6e1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190803/59892314</a><br />\n<br />\n 2019年08月03日<br />\n【逆權運動】網上流傳8.4實施戒嚴 港府澄清全屬謠言 <br />\n<br />\n近日網上流言香港將於8月4日實施戒嚴，特區政府發言人今日澄清並無此事，指有關說法全屬謠言。<br />\n<br />\n正在流亡美國的中國富商郭文貴日前於其YouTube直播中表示，自己獲得中共內部訊息，中共下達對香港執行戒嚴令，初步計畫是在8月4日至6日執行，戒嚴法規定是根據國家安全法、中共解放軍駐港法，「應香港政府之要求」，對香港實施戒嚴。<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴指在香港戒嚴期間，限制市民只准出境不進入境，起居飲食、醫療治安由戒嚴指揮部統一指揮，並會對駐港機構和外籍人士「清理」，同時展開自6月9日以來上街抗爭人士進行搜捕。"},{"pid":"7cf7bcb4c4a22b63189508171e01331d4dcc2ddd","tid":1399350,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"WSJ：郭文貴係北京間諜<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1351650/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1351650/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"86efffc0ececc330229058cf766f20a22effaac5","tid":1399350,"uid":271199,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:52:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />郭生次次都係吹水呃like"},{"pid":"5e896bac10f636d4e68a8c4d47225d88e8192fbb","tid":1399350,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:55:30.000Z","msg":"戒鹽了<img src=\"/as